OL,3,CFormer supply teacher admits taking
OL,4,Cupskirt photos of pupils
OL,6,FA former supply teacher has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to taking more than 100 upskirt
OL,8,Fphotos of pupils.
OL,10,FAbusali Rahman, 36, who worked at
OL,11,Fschools across the North West,
OL,12,Fadmitted 21 offences at Bolton Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
