CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779981069
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher admits taking
OL,4,Cupskirt photos of pupils
OL,6,FAppearing via videolink from HMP
OL,7,FAltcourse, he pleaded guilty to 12
OL,8,Fcounts of taking indecent photographs
OL,9,Fof children by upskirting, four counts
OL,10,Fof publishing an obscene article,
OL,11,Fthree counts of making indecent
OL,12,Fphotographs of children, one count of
OL,13,Fvoyeurism and one count of
OL,14,Fdistributing an indecent photograph of
OL,15,Fa child.
OL,17,FRahman, a British national of
OL,18,FBangladeshi ethnicity from Salford,
OL,19,Fwill be sentenced on September 1.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
