PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779981069
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher admits taking
OL,4,Cupskirt photos of pupils
OL,6,FEmma Kehoe, defending, said: "Mr
OL,7,FRahman knows this is a prison sentence
OL,8,Fbut he was going through a mental
OL,9,Fhealth crisis at the time."
OL,11,FShe asked for a psychiatric report
OL,12,Fahead of sentence.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police said Rahman
OL,15,Fwas arrested in June 2025 after a
OL,16,Fparent raised concerns when an image
OL,17,Fof their child in school uniform was
OL,18,Fcirculated on social media.
OL,26,@nD@^OUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
