PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779981069
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher admits taking
OL,4,Cupskirt photos of pupils
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Simon France said the guilty
OL,8,Fpleas were the result of a
OL,9,F"painstaking, thorough investigation".
OL,11,FHe said: "We first received reports of
OL,12,FAbusali Rahman's suspected offending
OL,13,Fin March 2025 and he was arrested in
OL,14,FJune that year.
OL,16,F"The offences are alleged to have
OL,17,Ftaken place in several secondary
OL,18,Fschools across the North West between
OL,19,FDecember 2023 and 2025.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@eO]sD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
