PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779981069
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher admits taking
OL,4,Cupskirt photos of pupils
OL,6,F"The officers and staff working on
OL,7,Fthis investigation, including our
OL,8,Fvictim identification team, have put
OL,9,Feverything into building a case
OL,10,Fagainst Rahman and bringing the
OL,11,Fcharges against him.
OL,13,F"This included our digital
OL,14,Finvestigation unit which has analysed
OL,15,Faround 1,000 images over the past
OL,16,Fyear."
OL,18,FHe said police had been in contact
OL,19,Fwith all the schools Rahman had worked
OL,20,Fin since he became a qualified teacher
OL,21,Fin 2023.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
